OL,5, An Ecuadorean mayor has been shot dead 
OL,6, and a bystander killed in an attack    
OL,7, while he toured his city.              
OL,9,FAgustin Intriago was hit several times 
OL,10,Fby a lone gunman in Manta on Sunday.   
OL,11,FAriana Estefania Chancay, a local      
OL,12,Ffemale footballer, also died.          
OL,14,FIntriago's wife, Rosita Saldarriagas,  
OL,15,Fsaid her heart and that of her children
OL,16,Fhad been "torn out" by the murder.     
OL,18,FPolice have yet to confirm a motive but
OL,19,Fsaid that Mr Intriago had reported     
OL,20,Freceiving threats.                     
